author: pburba
msg: Fix false copy test failures due to reliance on added path notification order.
Follow-up to r21152.  Python tests should not rely on a specific
notification order of paths when running svn add as the order of
these paths is ultimately tied to apr_dir_read() which does not
to None when calling run_and_verify_svn() to add paths.  Instead,
confirm paths were added correctly with run_and_verify_status().
